title: #92Noon! Friday Feast
description: A FEAST! Mary Kay Cabot joins during first hour with Browns/Kevin Stefanski intel, Chad Greenway in studio most of the middle hour, Indy Star Colts insider Jim Ayello on this weekend's game, Darrell Thompson on Gophers/Big10 return to play, a Russo cameo on Mikko Koivu's retirement, Feast Five picks and more!
